Track:
    target seek-location sync sync
    do
       time robot-sensor-now > if
          fire-robot-sensor sync
          robot-found if
             robot-position target! 
                     Transmit^ Attack& jump
          else
             fire-shot-sensor sync
             shot-found  if 
